These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: white, azure, lilac, blood-red, mauve, ivory, light-blue
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
There 7 different types of food: zucchini, radish, peach, blueberry, potato, pumpkin, orange
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the dutch##1
 3. the person eating potato is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the british is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the person who likes azure is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person eating orange is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the person eating blueberry is between the person eating orange and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person eating peach##1
10. the person who likes lilac is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who likes mauve##1
12. the person who likes mauve is the person eating zucchini##1
13. the person who likes white is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the person eating peach##1
15. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the german##1
16. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Color      | azure  | ivory        | mauve | lilac      | blood-red     | white      | light-blue     |
| Nationality   | british | dutch         | german   | australian | french    | egyptian | chinese |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding | baseball | basketball | swimming  | surfing  | golf    |
| Food     | potato  | pumpkin         | zucchini     | radish    | peach | blueberry     | orange     |

