 3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person traveling to rome is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person traveling to boston##2
11. the owner of the fish is the person traveling to colone##1
12. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
13. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person traveling to boston and the owner of the frog##2
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
17. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
18. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
19. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
